<body><bold>Token Assembler<end>
<tab><RECIPE name=blockTokenAssembler domain=Hivetera>
One day a shrine priest stared into the Hunger and contemplated it's uses. To help him understand the Hunger, the Token Assembler was created, though it is unknown who had created it. Either by his own genius or guidance by the unknown, the priest used experimentation and the use of sacrifices, and soon became the founder of the Tokens. All one needs to do is place the Assembler, then surround it with chests or another type of container with resources in it.
